OL,3,CMum's bid to find missing son who
OL,4,Cvanished on Italian island
OL,6,FHis shorts, T-shirt and trainers were
OL,7,Flater found on a wall near the
OL,8,Fvolunteer site. His phone, laptop and
OL,9,FID were left in his rucksack inside
OL,10,Fthe tent.
OL,12,FMichael's mum Cristina Pittalis says
OL,13,FSardinia's Forest Guard is searching
OL,14,Ffor her son alongside police and
OL,15,Ffirefighters.
OL,17,FHe is described as around 5ft 7ins
OL,18,Ftall and has long brown hair with
OL,19,Fshaved sides.
