OL,3,CMum's bid to find missing son who
OL,4,Cvanished on Italian island
OL,6,FHis mother said: "He is a very sweet
OL,7,Fboy, you can approach him without
OL,8,Ffear, please, if you see him stop him,
OL,9,Ftalk to him, but don't leave him
OL,10,Falone."
OL,12,FShe said she is "distraught, worried
OL,13,Fand upset", particularly as the area
OL,14,Fhe was last in is remote, exposed,
OL,15,Fvery hot and has treacherous cliff
OL,16,Fdrops.
